postContent: I love animals, but dogs are my favorite! They’re loyal, loving, and always good for a nose boop!
Summertime is the best time of the year! All the sunshine puts me in such a good mood!
Has anyone else seen the new Spiderman movie, ‘Across the Spiderverse’? Movie of the year! So good!
Couldn't help myself!!
Can’t wait for the Jordan 1 UNC shock drop this week, I’ve wanted a pair of those forever!
I’ve built so many machines on Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom, I think I’m going to apply for a mechanical engineering position at a local company.
I miss the Rainforest Café, it was always so fun to go when I was a kid! I still have their branded glasses from our trip in 2006!
I saw Star Wars: A New Hope when it first came out in 77! The scene when Luke destroys the Death Star still gets me out of my seat!
We made it to the beach! Happy summer, everyone!
Can I be honest? Toby McGuire was the best Spiderman. Those early 2000’s movies were AMAZING!
There’s nothing better than going to the mall to pick up some new clothes and accessories. Fashion really is my passion!
My collection is getting out of control, I think I need to get another shelving unit for all my shoes! I don’t even have time to wear them all!
That most recent Nintendo Direct was so cool! I loved how the new Mario games look, especially the new Super Mario Wonder game!
I actually visited the Amazon rainforest on vacation, and it was a life changing experience. What an incredible place!
I was so excited when they built the new dog park in 2018, my pups love going there to play with the other dogs!
I have two dogs, their names are Bali and Sugar! They’re best friends and such good pups!
Unfortunately, the new Star Wars trilogy is pretty mid, especially Episode IX. Woof!
I really want to go to the beach later to soak in the sun. Who wants to go with me?
My comic book collection is looking really good right now. Just picked up issue #14 of ‘The Amazing Spider-Man’ with Green Goblin’s debut!
I heard Gucci is finally moving in to the mall! I’m so excited, they are literally my FAVORITE luxury brand on earth. Can’t wait to go!!
I love Jordan IV’s and Jordan VI’s, but the original Jordan 1 Chicago is my favorite sneaker of all time. Will never go out of style.
Just got my new Lego Millennium Falcon coffee table! Such an awesome piece for the mancave!
We need to take better care of our environment for future generations! It’s our responsibility!
I’ve been playing Mario Kart since it came out on Nintedo64. That game never gets old, and it’s always fun! I always play as Lemmy!
